description:
FANTASY ABDUCTION:
Harmony has always had a fantasy of being abducted and sexual dominated by her captors. Not one to leave a girls fantasy unfufilled I set out to create the ultimate fantasy abduction for her.
Stranded on the side of the road. Car broken down in the snow. Cold. Wet. Helpless. Harmony waits for help, but winds up in the back of our van instead.
title: Ariel X, Annie Cruz, Princess Donna Dolore and Harmony
